## Trying the knowledge graph

GitNodes ships a read-only MCP server (`gitnodes mcp <brain>`). The example brain
in `examples/demo-brain` carries its own `.mcp.json` / `.cursor/mcp.json`: open
that folder as the workspace to let an agent traverse it with `search_brain`,
`list_nodes`, `read_node`, and `node_links`.
